2008-11-25  Brad Taylor  <brad@getcoded.net>

	* Adapter.cs: Add concept of an Adapter that manages it's own
	lifecycle, e.g.: isn't removed by HandleBulkRemove.  This is mainly
	used for "fake" widgets.

